trans-unit.source: Any LegacySettings node already present in the runsettings will be removed.
trans-unit.target: RunSettings 内に既に存在するすべての LegacySettings ノードは削除されます。

trans-unit.source: RunSettings does not contain an embedded testSettings, not migrating.
trans-unit.target: RunSettings には埋め込み testSettings が含まれていないため、移行されません。

trans-unit.source: The migrated RunSettings file has been created at: {0}
trans-unit.target: 移行された RunSettings ファイルは次の場所に作成されました: {0}

trans-unit.source: The attributes agentNotRespondingTimeout, deploymentTimeout, scriptTimeout of Timeouts node are not supported, so these will not be migrated.
trans-unit.target: Timeouts ノードの agentNotRespondingTimeout、deploymentTimeout、scriptTimeout 属性はサポートされていないため、これらは移行されません。

trans-unit.source: Valid usage: SettingsMigrator.exe <Full path to testsettings file or runsettings file to be migrated> SettingsMigrator.exe <Full path to testsettings file or runsettings file to be migrated> <Full path to runsettings file to be created> Examples: SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyTestSettings.testsettings SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyOldRunSettings.runsettings SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyTestSettings.testsettings E:\MyTest\MyNewRunSettings.runsettings SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyOldRunSettings.runsettings E:\MyTest\MyNewRunSettings.runsettings
trans-unit.target: 有効な使用法: SettingsMigrator.exe <Full path to testsettings file or runsettings file to be migrated> SettingsMigrator.exe <Full path to testsettings file or runsettings file to be migrated> <Full path to testsettings file or runsettings file to be migrated> 例: SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyTestSettings.testsettings SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyOldRunSettings.runsettings SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyTestSettings.testsettings E:\MyTest\MyNewRunSettings.runsettings SettingsMigrator.exe E:\MyTest\MyOldRunSettings.runsettings E:\MyTest\MyNewRunSettings.runsettings
